description: Retrieves all Amazon OpenSearch Service-managed VPC endpoints associated with a particular domain.

parameters.name: DomainName
parameters.description: The name of the domain to list associated VPC endpoints for.

nested_items.name: VpcEndpointSummaryList
nested_items.description: Information about each endpoint associated with the domain.

nested_items.name: VpcEndpointId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the endpoint.

nested_items.name: DomainArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the domain associated with the endpoint.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The current status of the endpoint.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: When nextToken is returned, there are more results available. The value of nextToken is a unique pagination token for each page. Send the request again using the returned token to retrieve the next page.
